    Use integer wavenumbers (not physical wavenumbers divided by dx):
    ```python
    k  = torch.fft.fftfreq(N, d=1.0/N)   # integer wavenumbers: [0,1,...,N/2-1,-N/2,...,-1]
    kr = torch.fft.rfftfreq(N, d=1.0/N)  # [0, 1, ..., N/2]
